product.name: Informix Client-SDK
product.feature:
Includes all components of Informix Client-SDK
This feature contains the files required to install Informix Object Interface for C++
This feature contains the files required to install Informix Object Interface for C++ Demos
This feature contains the files required to install Informix ESQL/C
This feature contains demos for Informix ESQL/C
Libraries to use applications with Informix SQL 7.2 and earlier versions
This feature contains the files required to install Informix LIBDMI for Client Applications
This feature contains the files required to install Informix ODBC Driver
This feature contains demos for Informix ODBC Driver
Informix common database administration utilities such as dbaccess

The feature contains files to support languages, cultural conventions, and code sets. These files are not required if your default locale uses American English, which is the default language in Informix when no GLS feature is installed.
Danish, Dutch, English, Finnish, French, German, Icelandic, Italian, Norwegian, Portuguese, Spanish, and Swedish locales
Czech, Polish, Russian, and Slovak locales
Traditional Chinese and simplified Chinese locales
Japanese locales
Korean locales
Thai locales
